  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Romance, relief, pleasure and the bliss of being steps from the Atlantic Ocean. If you're looking for happiness, you'll find it at the Allegria. Twenty-five miles from New York City and worlds away, an oceanfront oasis awaits you in Long Beach, New York. The Allegria is a luxurious seaside resort offering the best of everything. 143 airy beach-chic rooms, a rooftop pool and deck (Opening August 2009) the incomparable Joseph Christopher for Beauty &amp; Wellness (Opening Winter 2009) , Chef Todd Jacobs' world-famous, gourmet cuisine and endless views of the Atlantic. For oceanfront weddings, corporate events and meetings, family celebrations and special occasions, there is no more exquisite venue than the Allegria Hotel &amp; Spa. With a 200-seat ballroom, an exquisite Atrium and Chef Todd Jacob's new Atlantica at the Allegria and his L'Onda lounge overlooking Long Beach's famous boardwalk, The Allegria is becoming the most coveted beachfront location on Long Island for special events.

Facility Includes :
- High-speed Internet access: $12.95 (fee subject to change)
- 37" flat-panel LCD televisions
- 24 hour in-room dining
- Complimentary copy of either The New York Times, Wall Street Journal or USA Today delivered to your room
- Mini refrigerator
- Secured room safe
- Heated rooftop pool
- Complimentary 24/7 fitness center
- The Spa - Joseph Christopher for Beauty &amp; Wellness
- Atlantica at the Allegria Restaurant
- L'Onda Lounge &amp; rooftop lounge</Text>
  </Description>
